  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>App:</strong> ADHD House Planner<br>
  <strong>Last updated:</strong> March 17, 2026</p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>ADHD House Planner is a simple household task planner designed for people with ADHD. Your privacy is important to us.</p>

  <h2>Data We Collect</h2>
  <h3>What we store locally on your device</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Room and task preferences</li>
    <li>Task completion history</li>
    <li>Settings (optional name, language, default time)</li>
  </ul>
  <p>All data is stored exclusively on your device using SQLite and AsyncStorage. <strong>No data is transmitted to external servers.</strong> If you uninstall the app, all data is permanently deleted.</p>

  <h3>What we do NOT collect</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>We do <strong>not</strong> collect personal information</li>
    <li>We do <strong>not</strong> track your location</li>
    <li>We do <strong>not</strong> share data with third parties</li>
    <li>We do <strong>not</strong> use analytics or tracking services</li>
    <li>We do <strong>not</strong> require an account or login</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Advertising</h2>
  <p>The App displays banner advertisements provided by <strong>Google AdMob</strong>. AdMob may collect device identifiers and usage data as described in
  <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
  <p>We request <strong>non-personalized ads only</strong>. You can learn more about how Google uses information at:<br>
  <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank">https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites</a></p>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>This app is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children.</p>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by updating the "Last updated" date above.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, contact us at:<br>
  <a href="mailto:annunziatoco@gmail.com">annunziatoco@gmail.com</a></p>

